OL,5,G1550 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe second visit of the week is to
OL,7,     FSutton Park in Blackpool, run by
OL,8,     FStewart and Gill. Kelly and Serena
OL,9,     Fare blown away by the bling, but
OL,10,     FDebra and Jamie have cleanliness
OL,11,     Fconcerns.
OL,12,G1620 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FDebra and Jamie host at Tottington
OL,14,     FManor in Edburton, West Sussex.
OL,15,     FBut Gill doesn't like the
OL,16,     Fcountryside setting or her room,
OL,17,     Fand low scores at feedback lead to
OL,18,     Fcries of foul play.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
