OL,5,G1750 George Clarke's Old House New Home
OL,6,     FGeorge is out and about with his
OL,7,     Fsledgehammer, knocking holes in a
OL,8,     Ffake Tudor ceiling in Leamington
OL,9,     FSpa and moving doors in a
OL,10,     Ffarmhouse on the edge of the Peak
OL,11,     FDistrict.
OL,12,G1855 Location, Location, Location
OL,13,     FIn Oxfordshire, Phil has an uphill
OL,14,     Fbattle with Tan and Steve, who
OL,15,     Fwant open-plan living and kerb
OL,16,     Fappeal in a pricey patch. And can
OL,17,     FKirstie end indecisive Reena's
OL,18,     Ffive-year search?
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
