OL,5,G2200 24 Hours in A&E
OL,6,     FGrandmother Rose, who's 80, has
OL,7,     Ffluid on her lungs and is having
OL,8,     Ftrouble breathing, and 55-year-old
OL,9,     Ftrucker Kevin has serious injuries
OL,10,     Fafter his lorry rolled down a
OL,11,     Fverge.
OL,12,G2305 24 Hours in A&E
OL,13,     FNeil is flown in by helicopter
OL,14,     Fafter a head-on road collision,
OL,15,     Fand Matias needs help after
OL,16,     Ftrapping his hands in a train door
OL,17,     Fand being dragged along the
OL,18,     Fplatform.
