OL,12,G0325 A Place in the Sun
OL,13,     FBen Hillman house-hunts around
OL,14,     FGran Alacant on the Costa Blanca
OL,15,     Fwith Mick and Dianne from
OL,16,     FNewcastle. With a #120,000 budget,
OL,17,     Fthe couple are ready to make a
OL,18,     Fpermanent move to the sun.
